We're gonna install TailwindCSS. 
```bash
npm init -y
```

```bash
npm install tailwindcss postcss-cli autoprefixer  
touch styles.css
```

```css
/* styles.css */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

```bash
touch postcss.config.js 
```

```js
// postcss.config.js
module.exports = {
  plugins: [require('tailwindcss'), require('autoprefixer')]
};
```

´´´
// package.json
  "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
    "build": "postcss styles.css -o src/styles.css",
    //"dev": "npm run build"
  }
´´´

```bash
npx tailwindcss init 
```

```js
// tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  purge: [
     './src/**/*.html',
     './src/**/*.js',
   ],
  darkMode: false, // or 'media' or 'class'
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  variants: {},
  plugins: [],
}
```

